headline: Auto retail sector: Portfolio manager shares his top 2 picks
summary: Markets (^GSPC, ^IXIC, ^DJI) have been volatile in 2025 as investors continue to watch tariffs, geopolitical risks, and inflation. Hennessy Focus Fund co-portfolio manager Brian Macauley joins Market Domination Overtime to explain why he's eyeing long-term opportunities in the auto retail sector, including CarMax (KMX) and O'Reilly (ORLY). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.

headline: Up 55,810%, Is O'Reilly Automotive Stock Still a Buy?
summary: Fresh off a 15-for-1 stock split, can O'Reilly Automotive stock continue trouncing the market?  If you had invested $10,000 into O'Reilly Automotive (NASDAQ: ORLY) in 1993, you would have $5.59 million today.  Typically, investors associate this type of massive growth with disruptive technology companies pioneering brand-new industries.
